 libarchiver authors
 ===================

libarchiver is the archiver utility implemented in the library form that uses
the libminCrypt for the encryption/decryption of the data stored in the archive.
The compression is optional only when you provide password and optional salt
values. 

The algorithm was both written and implemented by:

	Michal Novotny <mignov@gmail.com>

If you want to contribute to the algorithm feel free to post patches to
the address/maintainer address written above and you'll be listed as one
of the authors as well.
